.subsubsection Staff Preferences - Workcenter

.bold Show only recent documents

If Checked, then only documents which have hit the inbox in the last month are displayed.

This interval is currently not user configurable but could be made so if someone makes this a 'feature request'.

.bold User must finalise all tasks

If checked, then all tasks generated by the user in the task manager, must be finalised by the user.

This can be over-ridden in the task manager for individual case.s
